	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Wed, Jun 12th 4:06 PM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=119627><span id=Sage>Kedr</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>59 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.40]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Every wonder that question?&nbsp;&nbsp;It looks like a few people have reading this thread.<br><br>Level bonus = (level - 25 / 2)<br><br>Max damage = (weapon skill + strength / 100) x (weapon damage + level bonus)<br><br>My 24 War example  (35 + 146 / 100) x (28 + 0) = 50.68 damage.  51 is what he max hits for also.<br><br>This has worked for me with all my weapons, critical hits and crippiling blows excluded.  </p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
