k about it.  If I am the only Warrior on a raid that does 2HB and a no-drop 2HB War only wpn drops, guess who gets it?  Skip the lotto, it goes to me.  Not being greedy or anything, I just believe in being well rounded in all wpns skills and not the dual-wield warrior that only ever touches 1HS or maybe 2HS because somehow it is more "manly".<br><br></p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=899422" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=899422</a><br>EClapton<br>66th Human Bard<br>Leader, Holy Might Guild<br>Seventh Hammer</td></tr>
